reviews.text: Rich, robust & velvety smooth â€” this kopi C had the perfect balance of strength & comfort. Full-bodied with a mellow finish, it was just what I needed to reset my afternoon. Not too acidic, not too bitter, just incredibly satisfying. A go-to brew for any time from noon to evening.

Stall owners not so fluent in English more fluent in Chinese. I think they speak Vietnamese? Tried their Honey Longan Soda, Large for $3.60, 25% honey not too sweet v nice! They also have toast, coffee and tea
